sentences: Matt Hires (born August 5, 1985) is an American singer-songwriter from Tampa, Florida.
As a cabinet store worker by day and a musician by night, Hires always had a heroic passion for music.

Hires released his debut EP, Live From the Hotel Cafe, under F-Stop Music/Atlantic Records, on October 7, 2008.
section: == Live From the Hotel Café, EP ==

sentences: Building his fan base in preparation for his debut album, Hires appeared at the SXSW Music Festival and on the 2009 Mayercraft Carrier.

sentences: On July 28, 2009 Hires released his debut full-length album, Take Us to the Start, featuring his first single, "Honey Let Me Sing You A Song."
